claims.sentence: The RadSimPE software program5 was used to simulate the radiology workstation environment, a screenshot of this application is shown in Fig. 1.
The study protocol is summarized in Fig. 2.

The ability of subjects to identify pulmonary nodules on CXR (NodDetect) showed statistically significant improvement for both control and experimental groups, greater in the experimental groups, but the difference between groups was not statistically significant, ROC curves shown in Fig. 3, -value = 0.634.
The survey response frequency polygons are shown in Fig. 4.
